Our Perfect Wedding (OPW) viewers have spoken, they want Nomsa “Gomora Diva” Buthelezi-Shezi to present all the episodes of the wedding show. On Sunday, 3 July, Lebogang “The Funny Chef” Tlokana hosted Nkanyiso and Zandile’s wedding. By the end of the show, the viewers had decided that she’s not a doing a good job for OPW as a result they took turns demanding that Gomora Diva is brought back. Fuzelihle Ngcobo commented: “The host is good, but not for Our Perfect Wedding. I can imagine those comments from Gomora Diva about the bride being a virgin.” ALSO READ : Bonang’s tweet divides tweeps! Sinentokozo Mtetwa said: “No, can we allow Lebo to continue with other shows. This one is just not in her. She arrives under-dressed and struggles to even be excited and jovial. Gomora Diva must do all the episodes, please. Zelda said: “She’s the most boring TV presenter ever.” Nonto Sangweni said: “So happy Sis Nomsa is coming back next week because Lebo didn’t do any justice to this show. She’s boring shame.” The Funny Chef joined OPW this year and she alternates with Vele Manenje and Gomora Diva.